483
00:49:07,644 --> 00:49:11,512
-You got a phone call at the store.
-All right.

484
00:49:35,605 --> 00:49:38,199
-Hello.
-Jon, is that you?

485
00:49:38,375 --> 00:49:41,970
-Paula.
-What the hell is going on?

486
00:49:42,145 --> 00:49:44,136
