492
00:49:58,962 --> 00:50:04,491
Look, I'll come home.
Let's figure this out. Meet me.

493
00:50:05,969 --> 00:50:07,402
Jon?

494
00:50:09,072 --> 00:50:10,733
Jon?

495
00:50:12,142 --> 00:50:15,942
