496
00:50:17,147 --> 00:50:19,172
Hello?

497
00:50:20,283 --> 00:50:22,717
Hello? Now--

498
00:51:51,108 --> 00:51:53,303
You're not barking.

499
00:51:58,548 --> 00:51:59,572
Who are you?.

500
00:52:00,917 --> 00:52:03,784
-Jon Katz.
-Right.

501
